description: This Chainlink VRF top 10% score Gaston purrs with a rating of 34, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 170, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Leverage for East, 1 for South, and 1 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60345-66110-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [170 Votes, Top 10% Score]
